Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家总是说星空无比美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 我却没有对星空的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说厌恶 不如说是有种畏惧的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我无法正视星空的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 星空对我来说 就如深邃的黑暗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有了那样守护着我的人 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这个城镇的人口有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2040人 到今日为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈哈 那可真是不错 那可真是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始 我的收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会达到2040个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真是不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石榴…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量涌上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,short cu…咳 咳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能话说多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接力 那家伙和我一样是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有秋名才能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操控的方法是一样的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有什么事吗 土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿是我的城镇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 土地神不是不能掺和的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有说过吗 交给那些孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…停电…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候 不要东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭助带着手铐竟然还那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的 那孩子不可能伤害镇上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该 你拯救不了任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 请退下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把铃还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把铃还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我很快就会一起操纵你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的血和肉体 都不会让你任意驱使的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭助 秋名住手 恭助他…秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 能动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪气调律 秋名爷爷的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然控制有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的秋名的话 能拯救那个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会要你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子已经被弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使用的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了…讨厌 讨厌大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最讨厌大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追石榴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 这样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃好像讨厌这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧 没有救人意识的家伙即使去了也只是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓝 就拜托你带路了～好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 老板娘 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 开始休息一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以决定担任镇长助手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为你建设城镇的信念和气魄所折服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城镇很棒 有自信就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 铃说了讨厌大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 铃说的不是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城镇里住着的人们知道的 包括在这住了10年的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯太的婆婆 现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在呢 在城镇尽头的文化馆里 所有的镇民都在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所有的人 在开茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要做的话就能做好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是姬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一起愉快的喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 什么来着 完事了就过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚六爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 见到铃的话告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的午饭是新做的拉面两份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也预定一份可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那就三份 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 铃在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有拿出王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 铃都说了不想呆在这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃为什么来到这个城镇 忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被送往另一个世界里痛苦的活着 所以才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是和店长你们一起生活以后 一次也没有说要回到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我不会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石榴 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我学了好多菜 给你做许多菜 我很有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 纠缠不休的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样下去无法靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓝 在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神干涉的话 能达到传心术的效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是简单的事情的话就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天魔传声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭助 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘀咕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 住手吧 我和石榴一起离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 铃 回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和石榴一起生活 这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都住手吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命挣扎是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还在这座城镇战斗 就不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还被这座城镇 居民和龙宠爱着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有龙枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是龙枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方竟然有龙脉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩个人一起生活吧 我保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还在被人保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直讨厌星空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 此刻 想要去保护的此刻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得肯定不会感到恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 最后睁开眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的 美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋…为什么大家跟来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…一不注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落下去啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做垫子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就让我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 让我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就让我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我担心啊 想和铃在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论 无论铃多么讨厌我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋名 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然晦气都除尽了 还是带去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 今晚回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不坦诚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 像大家那样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无顾忌的玩闹 不承担自己的责任是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是镇长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在开始才辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后 越来越多的猎人会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着不杀生情绪的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.16,0:24:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅要击退他们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.49,0:24:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不得不接受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.09,0:24:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.63,0:24:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有欢乐和干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙儿希望这座城镇幸福呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:25:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 做为镇长 全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.89,0:25:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.56,0:25:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬果然很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.19,0:25:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话 有了半妖朋友可是很高兴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.62,0:25:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是姬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.17,0:25:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住证
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.42,0:25:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 太好了 石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.34,0:25:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现金支票就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.47,0:25:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.56,0:25:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.85,0:25:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家认为很美丽的星空我最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.40,0:25:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在有了可以一同仰望的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.65,0:25:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 铺被了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.53,0:25:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的星空也非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.66,0:26:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
